Package: aegis-siem-agent
Version: 1.0.0
Section: net
Priority: optional
Architecture: amd64
Depends: python3 (>= 3.11), python3-pip, systemd
Maintainer: Mokshit Bindal <mokshit@aegis-siem.dev>
Description: Aegis SIEM Agent - Lightweight Security Monitoring Agent
 Aegis SIEM Agent collects system metrics, logs, commands, and process
 information and forwards them to the Aegis SIEM server for analysis
 and anomaly detection.
 .
 Features:
  - Real-time system metrics collection (CPU, memory, disk, network)
  - Command logging and monitoring
  - Process monitoring
  - Log file monitoring
  - Secure JWT-based authentication
  - Auto-registration with server
  - Minimal resource footprint
Homepage: https://github.com/MokshitBindal/Aegis
